ink，咁樣互相協助先會改善被忽視既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n9)<span style=\"color: red;\">發現QUOTE長度過長請係回覆時刪減不必要的字　減少QUOTE過長的情況</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">永遠都係少女時代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家繼續加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"9a87a126703afe4982e8ce6dae92ef12d774352d","tid":278783,"uid":5976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:09:35.000Z","msg":"大獲...開錯吹水台...<br />\n我開過..."},{"pid":"1c50e0e5a594c763aa5e0e069559632546332b88","tid":278783,"uid":39587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:10:27.000Z","msg":"我想知今次香港場個歌單同首爾場係咪一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 好彩13年個支棒仲有電 聽日帶埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aef5a35aa2a6ee47ded449c4eb8887b57b35db7","tid":278783,"uid":33439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:11:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想知今次香港場個歌單同首爾場係咪一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 好彩13年個支棒仲有電 聽日帶埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n13年支棒暗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係無計照用住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821eefc473a336273238d7afbd62bbc4347388a3","tid":278783,"uid":82727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:13:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"55193f17fa9cb2c2f69c1f8aa49796e25ee7af1e","tid":278783,"uid":5976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:13:27.000Z","msg":"唔好推呢個POST~斬左佢KA LA~去返音樂台個POST度傾~"},{"pid":"20dc9ee3a33c2e9fde818de8473580cfc91676e2","tid